  <p>
  <h2> Fighting Games</h2>
  Hello fellow gamer if you are reading<br> this that means that means that you're<br> interested in video games but not just<br> any genre, the fighting game genre,<br> but fighting games!
  </p>
  <p>
  <h3>Some Info</h3>
    Fighting Games has been a very popular<br>
genre, due to it's competetive nature. Games<br>
like these are held in tournaments, for any <br>
willing competitor who would wish to compete<br>
against some of the best in their region. A<br>
winner would receive a reward in the form<br> of money, and recognition, which means they'll<br>
known for their skill as a competitive player.<br> Many people become professional due this this genre.
</p>
